---
title: 'Modal'
description: 'An overlaying window to take focus away from the current context.'
---

## Basic Example

```svelte
<script>
	import { Modal, ModalBackdrop, ModalContent, ModalDescription, ModalTitle, ModalTrigger } from 'lithesome';
</script>

<Modal>
	<ModalTrigger>Click me</ModalTrigger>

	<ModalBackdrop />
	<ModalContent>
		<ModalTitle>Modal Title</ModalTitle>
		<ModalDescription>Modal Description</ModalDescription>
	</ModalContent>
</Modal>
```
